<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>
Two adjoining fragments of a <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType"><rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> shaft</rs>, without moulding (together <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.46</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.08</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.42</measure>). The upper left corner survives as a separate fragment.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>
Inscribed on the face; the text must have begun on a crowning feature.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p>
<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure>; ligature, <foreign lang="grc">ΤΗ</foreign> l. 3.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0260" exact="both" notBefore="0253">A.D. 256-260</date>
(<rs type="criteria">content</rs>).</p>
</div>

<div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition">
<head lang="en">Edition</head>
<ab><lb n="0"/><gap dim="top" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="line"/><lb n="1"/><w lemma="ὁ">τὸν</w> <rs reg="epiphanestatos" type="dignity" key="epiphan"><w lemma="ἐπιφανής">ἐπ<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied>φα<supplied reason="lost">νέστα</supplied><lb n="2" type="worddiv"/>τoν</w></rs> <rs key="caesar" reg="caesar" type="official-secul"><persName type="emperor"><name reg="Καῖσαρ">Καίσα<supplied reason="lost">ρα</supplied></name></persName></rs><lb n="2a"/><space dim="vertical" extent="1" unit="line"/><lb n="3"/><w lemma="ὁ">ἡ</w> <rs reg="clarissimus" key="clarissimus" type="dignity"><w lemma="λαμπρός">λαμπροτά<hi rend="ligature">τη</hi></w></rs> <w lemma="Ἀφροδεισιεύς"><placeName type="ethnic" full="yes" reg="Ἀφροδεισιεύς">Ἀ<lb n="4" type="worddiv"/>φροδεισιέων</placeName></w> <rs reg="city" key="city" type="subject"><w lemma="πόλις">πό<lb n="5" type="worddiv"/> <g type="scroll"/>λις</w></rs> <g type="scroll"/>
</ab>
</div>

<div type="history" n="text-constituted-from">
<head>Text Constituted From</head>
<p>
Transcriptions (Reynolds, Roueché).</p>
</div>

<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>
<gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="line"/> the most renowned Caesar; the most splendid city of the Aphrodisians <supplied reason="subaudible">put up his statue</supplied>.</p>
</div>

<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>
See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="I.10">I.10</xref>.</p>
</div>

